HEADWORD: Doppelgänger
<hw>Dop"pel*g⟦aum⟧ng`er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[G.]</ety> <def>A spiritual or ghostly double or counterpart; esp.,
